===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Variant of {{och-l|气}}, distinguished to indicate a phonetically borrowed meaning “to beg”.

The top component of the character is unrelated to {{zh-l|*旅}}, {{zh-l|*傷}}, {{zh-l|*复}}, {{zh-l|*每}} as well as {{zh-l|*人}}.

